window.bookSummaryJSON = "<i>New York Times</i> best-selling author C. J. Box's <i>Below Zero</i> is the 10th novel featuring Wyoming game warden Joe Pickett. <p>The telephone calls from her stepdaughter April send chills down the spine of Joe's daughter Sherry. Wasn't April murdered six years ago in a bloody massacre? Wondering how this youthful caller knows details only April could know, Sherry becomes confused while Joe grows suspicious. Is the caller April - or are Joe and his family victims of a cruel hoax?</p>"; 
